Step-3 
 (Before connect, Setup your domain with joggata.com hosting  https://vimeo.com/1011948394/8773cbf4b9?fl=pl&fe=cm )
 
-	Connect PHISHING website with Landing Page
a.	go to joggata.com --> login
b.	Landing Page --> All landing page --> choose a PHISHING site 
 
c.	Click on “Apply your landing page” button and it will open a form
 
	Here , you need to setup below fields info
	- Domain: abc.xyz (select your work type domain)
	- Landing Page Link: copy and paste your created HV Link landing page url here
	- Folder Location: /game  (for game write “/game”, for health and beauty product write “/health”)
	
	Click on “SUBMIT” button to save
  
d.	Wait for approve (Maximum 7 days)
 
e.	To see landing page approved or not, go to joggata.com and login
 
f.	After approved, you will get final link
      https://abc.xyz/game

